%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hashemi.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFelt%20has%20pivoted%20to%20an%20AI-first%20platform%20where%20users%20type%20in%20a%20few%20natural%20language%20prompts%20to%20generate%20any%20application%20they%20need%2C%20such%20as%20maps%2C%20charts%2C%20and%20dashboards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222246%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Felt's%20AI%20driven%20platform.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6870d07b85e81483682dd254%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221676%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFelt's%20AI-driven%20platform%20can%20generate%20maps%20through%20user%20prompts.%3Cp%3EFelt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20has%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20use%20cases%20and%20customers%2C%20from%20NGOs%20to%20insurers%20and%20emergency%20responders.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20so%20many%20industries%2C%20from%20agriculture%20to%20construction%20to%20decarbonization%2C%20that%20use%20our%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20Hashemi%20said.%20Over%20half%20of%20its%20customers%20are%20in%20the%20energy%20and%20climate%20sector%2C%20he%20added%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20sustainable%20cement%20company%20Brimstone%2C%20which%20is%20using%20Felt%20to%20help%20build%20a%20more%20sustainable%20concrete%20analysis%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFelt's%20dashboards%20can%20also%20track%20metrics%20like%20deforestation%2C%20air%20quality%2C%20and%20flood%20risk.%20The%20startup's%20tech%20has%20been%20used%20to%20monitor%20and%20detect%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-01-21%2Fla-fires-bolster-investment-case-for-climate-adaptation-technology%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildfires%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20crisis%20that%20has%20alarmed%20insurers%20and%20utility%20companies%20and%20encouraged%20them%20to%20adopt%20more%20high-tech%20mitigation%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorthern%20Arizona%20State%20University%20has%20used%20Felt%20to%20build%20a%20fire-preven