_blank%5C%22%3EF-1%20visa%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%20and%202017%2C%20my%20company%20tried%20twice%20to%20get%20me%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fh-1b-visa-helped-build-career-what-people-get-wrong-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EH-1B%20visa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20step%20toward%20permanent%20residency%20in%20the%20US.%20Petitions%20are%20chosen%20for%20processing%20through%20a%20lottery%20selection%20system%2C%20but%20I%20wasn't%20picked%20either%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20that%20time%2C%20I%20started%20to%20find%20out%20more%20information%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-reopens-green-card-applications-for-foreign-workers-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreen%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%20backlog%20for%20Indian%20nationals.%20There's%20a%20cap%20per%20country%20at%207%25%20of%20all%20the%20green%20cards%20allocated%20that%20year.%20India%20has%20a%20large%20population%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20applicants%2C%20so%20there%20is%20a%20very%20long%20waitlist%20to%20have%20your%20applications%20processed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20I%20was%20thrashing%20against%20the%20system%20just%20to%20be%20able%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20country%20and%20contribute.%20In%20a%20moment%20of%20clarity%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20wasn't%20willing%20to%20keep%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20I%20no%20longer%20had%20work%20authorization%20and%20had%20to%20stop%20working.%20I%20didn't%20like%20not%20making%20an%20income%20at%20all%2C%20and%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20hard-won%20career%20had%20been%20yanked%20away%20from%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8e96d07-0b7c-4732-b5de-d186f8cf6e5b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20moved%20to%20Canada%20as%20a%20permanent%20resident%20and%20have%20found%20a%20sense%20of%20belonging%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20temporary%20solution%2C%20I%20tried%20changing%20my%20status%20from%20an%20F-1%20to%20an%20F-2%20vis