20they'll%20'flip%20your%20company%20on%20its%20head'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aaron%20Levie%20at%20TechCrunch%20Disrupt%20San%20Francisco%202019%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61dde1844ede320018b70b69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBox%20CEO%20Aaron%20Levie%20says%20companies%20should%20hire%20AI-native%20graduates%20to%20stay%20competitive%20in%20a%20rapidly%20evolving%20field.%3Cp%3ESteve%20Jennings%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20TechCrunch%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBox%20CEO%20said%20AI-native%20graduates%20can%20outpace%20junior%20engineers%20and%20transform%20how%20companies%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAaron%20Levie%20urged%20firms%20to%20hire%20AI-fluent%20talent%20before%20rivals%20do%20in%20the%20escalating%20AI%20talent%20war.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20and%20Meta%20are%20offering%20massive%20incentives%20to%20capture%20AI%20talent.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20college%20graduates%20who%20are%20fluent%20in%20AI%20tools%20could%20become%20some%20of%20the%20most%20valuable%20hires%20at%20major%20companies%2C%20according%20to%20Box%20CEO%20Aaron%20Levie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHire%20a%20bunch%20of%20these%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20Monday%20interview%20on%20the%20a16z%20podcast%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20they're%20going%20to%20flip%20your%20company%20on%20its%20head%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20much%20faster%20the%20organization%20can%20run.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20graduating%2C%20the%20thing%20I%20would%20be%20selling%20to%20any%20corporation%20some%20way%20or%20another%20is%20that%20if%20you're%20AI-native%20right%20now%20coming%20out%20of%20college%2C%20the%20amount%20you%20can%20teach%20at%20a%20company%20is%20unbelievable%2C%26quot%3B%20Levie%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevie%2C%20who%20cofounded%20Box%20in%202005%20and%20now%20leads%20a%20company%20serving%20more%20than%2065%25%20of%20the%20Fortune%20500%2C%20said%20AI-literate%20graduates%20are%20better%20positioned%20to%20boost%20organizational%20efficiency%20than%20traditional%20junior%20engineers%2C%20and%20can%20do%20it%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20will%20be%20able%20to%20show%20companies%20way%20faster%20ways%20of%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20company%2C%20you%20should%20be%20prioritizing%20this%20talent%20that's%20just%20like%3A%20'Why%20does%20it%20take%20you%20guys%20two%20weeks%20to%20research%20a%20market%20to%20enter%3F%20I%20can%20do%20that%20in%20deep%20research%20and%20get%20an%20answer%20to%20you%20in%2030%20minutes.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%2C%20Cursor%2C%20and%20GitHub%20Copilot%20becoming%20standard%20in%20developer%20workflows%2C%20Levie%20said%20the%20newest%20generation%20of%20engineers%20will%20rely%20on%20them%20from%20day%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20incoming%20class%20of%20engineers%20that%20you%20hire%20%E2%80%94%20they%20will%20literally%20not%20be%20able%20to%20code%20without%20AI%20assisting%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20not%20100%25%20obvious%20that's%20a%20bad%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20tech%20veterans%20worry%20that%20AI%20tools%20will%20undermine%20foundational%20programming%20skills%2C%20Levie%20took%20a%20more%20pragmatic%20view%3A%20AI%20can%20speed%20up%20development%2C%20make%20software%20engineering%20more%20accessible%2C%20and%20help%20young%20engineers%20make%20meaningful%20contributions%20earlier%20in%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c44c963-1eea-4cc1-ba4e-934e68bbd29f%5C%22%3EThe%20AI%20talent%20war%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELevie's%20push%20to%20hire%20AI-native%20grads%20comes%20amid%20a%20full-blown%20talent%20war%20among%20tech's%20biggest%20players%20%E2%80%94%20and%20tensions%20are%20rising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20on%20his%20brother's%2