ecticut%20College%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20when%20the%20field%20was%20still%20relatively%20new.%20She%20said%20engagement%20with%20consumers%2C%20investors%2C%20and%20other%20stakeholders%20was%20a%20trend%20taking%20shape%20at%20the%20time%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20AIDS%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20I%20watched%20it%20take%20hold%20with%20environmentalists%2C%20with%20breast%20cancer%20survivors%2C%20with%20labor%20unions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20sort%20of%20rose%20up%20and%20felt%20that%20they%20had%20a%20say%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20social%20media%20further%20elevated%20the%20importance%20of%20corporate%20communications%2C%20Susman%20said%2C%20as%20companies%20needed%20help%20managing%20relations%20with%20the%20public%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20it%20was%20a%20legal%20battle%20that%20kicked%20off%20in%201996%20by%20her%20then-employer%20American%20Express%20against%20its%20rivals%20Visa%20and%20Mastercard%20over%20anti-competition%20allegations%20that%20underscores%20for%20her%20why%20corporate%20affairs%20is%20such%20a%20critical%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20successful%20conclusion%20of%20the%20lawsuit%20was%20really%20driven%20by%20a%20supportive%20communications%20and%20government-relations%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Susman%2C%20who%20was%20American%20Express's%20vice%20president%20of%20European%20corporate%20affairs%20at%20communications%20at%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20when%20I%20had%20the%20big%20%3Cem%3Eaha%3C%2Fem%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESusman%20has%20worked%20under%20nine%20chief%20executive%20officers%20throughout%20her%20career%2C%20including%20three%20at%20Pfizer.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20nothing%20more%20gratifying%20than%20having%20the%20honor%20of%20advising%20a%20CEO%20on%20their%20most%20pressing%20concerns%20and%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20rare%20air.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeirdre%20Latour%2C%20a