0are%20now%20in%20college.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20daughter%2C%2018%2C%20still%20lives%20at%20home%2C%20and%20my%20son%2C%2020%2C%20has%20moved%20out.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe're%20navigating%20this%20new%20time%20period%20and%20our%20shifting%20dynamic%2C%20and%20figuring%20out%20our%20new%20boundaries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParenting%20changes%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwealthy-parent-planning-paying-kids-go-to-college-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20head%20off%20to%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20dynamic%20shifts.%20It's%20a%20strange%20transitional%20time%2C%20and%20right%20now%2C%20I'm%20learning%20to%20let%20go.%20I%20am%20still%20a%20mom%2C%20but%20as%20my%20kids%20begin%20to%20transition%20to%20adulthood%2C%20there%20are%20also%20lessons%20I%20still%20need%20to%20teach%20them.%20I%20want%20them%20to%20know%20how%20to%20make%20doctor%20appointments%20and%20refill%20prescriptions.%20I%20want%20them%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20things%20without%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20four%20kids%2C%20including%20an%2018-year-old%20daughter%20and%20a%2020-year-old%20son.%20My%20relationships%20with%20both%20of%20them%20have%20changed%20since%20they%20started%20college%3B%20there%20are%20also%20differences%20in%20the%20dynamic%20between%20me%20and%20my%20daughter%2C%20who%20remains%20at%20home%20in%20the%20bedroom%20she%20grew%20up%20in%2C%20and%20my%20relationship%20with%20my%20son%2C%20who%20has%20moved%20out%20and%20now%20lives%20with%20his%20girlfriend.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b104369-272a-4ec9-b981-5c702ee91055%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe're%20figuring%20out%20this%20new%20period%20together%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20legally%2C%20they%20are%20adults%2C%20but%20they%20are%20still%20learning%20some%20monumental%20lessons%20that%20we%20are%20navigating%20both%20together%20and%20apart.%20We've%20alr