er.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e56ec417-4e36-4e40-a4da-8363ec2782fc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20our%20dynamic%20shifts%2C%20so%20do%20our%20boundaries%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20interesting%20issue%20is%20figuring%20out%20boundaries%20together%20%E2%80%94%20both%20theirs%20and%20mine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20college-age%20daughter%20can%20vote%20and%20get%20approved%20for%20a%20credit%20card%2C%20but%20still%20lives%20under%20our%20roof.%20We've%20decided%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpsychologist-parenting-teens-reminder-struggles-of-age-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20to%20impose%20a%20curfew%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20her.%20However%2C%20she%20does%20need%20to%20call%20me%20and%20let%20me%20know%20where%20she%20is.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20money%2C%20we've%20discussed%20what%20she%20pays%20for%20and%20what%20I%20cover.%20She%20works%2C%20and%20she%20pays%20for%20some%20of%20her%20clothes%20and%20activities%20while%20I%20cover%20her%20cellphone%20bill%20and%20anything%20related%20to%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20the%20house%2C%20like%20food%20and%20utilities.%20She%20also%20paid%20for%20most%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-mom-made-college-tours-exciting-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollege%20visit%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20we%20went%20on%20together%20to%20Arizona%2C%20including%20her%20flight.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThings%20work%20differently%20for%20her%20brother%2C%20who%20lives%20on%20his%20own.%20I%20don't%20set%20rules%20for%20him.%20The%20only%20bills%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-still-on-parents-cell-streaming-plans-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estill%20cover%20are%20his%20cellphone%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20medical%20bills.%20I%20