ch%20unicorn%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvey-legal-tech-startup-faces-growing-competition-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHarvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20Ironclad.%20It's%20in%20the%20long%20tail%20%E2%80%94%20what%20he%20describes%20as%20the%20Shopify%20phase%20of%20legal%20tech.%20Just%20as%20Amazon%20and%20Shopify%20unlocked%20a%20wave%20of%20entrepreneurs%20who%20built%20their%20own%20stores%20on%20top%20of%20those%20platforms%2C%20Abramowitz%20believes%20artificial%20intelligence%20will%20enable%20a%20surge%20of%20%26quot%3Bbionic%20boutiques%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20generate%20significantly%20more%20revenue%20per%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20much%20bigger%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthat%20inures%20to%20the%20benefit%20of%20more%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECovenant%20joins%20a%20growing%20list%20of%20software%20companies%20with%20big%20backers%20and%20even%20bigger%20promises%20to%20strip%20the%20drudgery%20from%20legal%20work.%20But%20murmurs%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flegal-ai-tech-boom-bubble-fear-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elegal%20tech%20bubble%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20growing%20louder%2C%20especially%20as%20flashy%20tools%20like%20Harvey%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmax-junestrand-legora-founder-legal-tech-ai-harvey-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELegora%3C%2Fa%3E%20jockey%20for%20relevance%20in%20a%20still-cautious%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20Covenant%20doesn't%20compete%20directly%20with%20those%20platforms%2C%20which%20sell%20into%20law%20firms%20and%20corporate%20legal%20departments.%20Instead%2C%20it%20occupies%20a%20lane%20closer%20to%20contract%20review%20tools%20like%20Luminance%20and%20Spellbook%2C%20which%20are%20also%20built%20for%20lawyers%2C%20not%20private%20market%20investors.%20To%20Berrent%2C%20the%20key%20distinction%20is%20that%20Covenant%20is%20selling%20legal%20services%20to%20customers%20who%20typically%20hire%20Big%20Law%20to%20do%20this%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBerrent%20says%20she%20sees%20the%20next%20big%20opportunity%20not%20in%20AI%20%3Cem%3Efor%3C%2Fem%3E%20law%20firms%2C%20but%20in%20entirely%20new%20firms%20built%20around%20the%20tech.%20Call%20it%20counsel-as-a-service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUber%20didn't%20sell%20software%20to%20taxi%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Instead%2C%20it%20redefined%20how%20people%20think%20about%20getting%20from%20point%20A%20to%20B.%20That's%20the%20kind%20of%20shift%20she's%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECorrection%3A%20An%20earlier%20version%20of%20this%20story%20misstated%20when%20Jen%20Berrent%20worked%20at%20WeWork.%20She%20was%20the%20chief%20legal%20officer%20from%202014%20to%202020%2C%20not%20during%20the%20late%20aughts.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20the%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amrussell%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emrussell%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20%40MeliaRussell.01.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20here's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweworks-former-top-lawyer-is-starting-an-ai-native-law-firm-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752573602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6875114985e81483682df285%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweworks-former-top-lawyer-is-starting-an-ai-native-law-firm-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Covenant%20wants%20to%20do%20for%20fund%20docs%20what%20TurboTax%20did%20for%20tax%20prep%3A%20make%20the%20old%20way%20look%20unnecessarily%20expens