f%20customer%20in%20mind.%20Sure%2C%20Tribeca%20is%20an%20affluent%20neighborhood%2C%20so%20we're%20expecting%20plenty%20of%20high-income%20shoppers%2C%20including%20families%20and%20investment%20bankers.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fciti-remote-work-two-weeks-august-hybrid-roles-jane-fraser-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECiti's%20headquarters%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20down%20the%20street%2C%20and%20Goldman%20Sachs%20and%20American%20Express%20are%20nearby.)%20But%2C%20I've%20also%20gotten%20comments%20from%20nurses%20and%20doctors%20who%20can't%20wait%20to%20come%20here%20on%20their%20lunch%20break%20or%20after%20their%20shift.%20I%20really%20do%20think%20it's%20diversified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20making%20some%20items%20on%20the%20menu%20more%20affordable%20to%20keep%20it%20inclusive.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20hearts%20of%20palm%20noodles%20are%20coming%20from%20Hawaii%2C%20and%20they're%20super%20expensive%20to%20source%2C%20so%20the%20menu%20items%20with%20those%20will%20cost%20more.%20The%20breakfast%20burritos%2C%20though%2C%20are%20easier%20to%20source%2C%20and%20we%20won't%20have%20to%20charge%20as%20much.%20I%20don't%20want%20the%20store%20to%20have%20an%20elitist%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20want%20people%20to%20think%20they%20can't%20come%20in%20here%20because%20it's%20too%20expensive.%20I%20want%20it%20to%20be%20a%20diverse%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeadow-lane-gourmet-grocery-store-nyc-opening-marketing-strategy-tiktok-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752573301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68717600f748d8c055f58044%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeadow-lane-gourmet-grocery-store-nyc-opening-marketing-strategy-tiktok-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sammy%20Nussdorf%20uses%20TikTok%20