al%20launched%20its%20own%20stablecoin%20called%20PayPal%20USD%20back%20in%202023.%20More%20recently%2C%20Mastercard%20announced%20in%20April%20a%20partnership%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcircle-stock-price-usd-coin-crypto-crcl-ipo-genius-act-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECircle%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20enable%20stablecoin%20payments%20on%20its%20merchant%20network%20using%20USDC%20for%20crypto-to-fiat%20conversions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShopping%20and%20payments%20services%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshopify-alters-revenue-share-exemption-impacting-app-developers-plans-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EShopify%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20the%20last%20area%20the%20bank%20flagged.%20The%20e-commerce%20platform%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20roll%20out%20USDC%20payments%20in%20partnership%20with%20Circle%20and%20expand%20its%20crypto%20checkout%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Poonawala%2C%20cross-border%20payments%20could%20be%20a%20prominent%20use%20case%20for%20stablecoins%20within%20the%20payments%20space.%20He%20believes%20Shopify's%20stablecoin%20features%20will%20allow%20merchants%20to%20connect%20more%20easily%20with%20global%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20take%20between%20three%20to%20five%20years%20to%20fully%20build%20out%20the%20infrastructure%20needed%20for%20widespread%20stablecoin%20adoption%2C%20according%20to%20Poonawala.%20But%20with%20a%20friendly%20legislative%20environment%20and%20increased%20attention%20from%20traditional%20banks%20and%20payment%20companies%2C%20stablecoins%20could%20become%20a%20disruptive%20force%20in%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstablecois-genius-act-crypto-week-ethereum-bitcoin-payments-bofa-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752571802000%2C%22visual%22%3A