20gives%20it%20a%20clear%20advantage%20over%20Tesla.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTesla%20should%20just%20accept%20that%20and%20do%20what%20they%20need%20to%20do%20to%20get%20the%20service%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%20%26quot%3BBut%20as%20of%20now%2C%20nobody%20has%20full%20self-driving%20software%20that%20actually%20is%20consistent%20enough%20to%20drive%20across%20a%20real%20town.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20those%20challenges%20and%20the%20revenue%20loss%20that%20could%20stem%20from%20the%20end%20of%20the%20EV%20tax%20credit%2C%20Gerber%20predicts%20more%20pain%20for%20the%20stock.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20stock%20is%20way%20overvalued%20and%20should%20trade%20in%20line%20with%20its%20Mag%207%20peers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20was%20trading%20at%20almost%20170x%20earnings%20on%20Monday.%20For%20comparison%2C%20Nvidia%20stock%20was%20trading%20at%2054x%20earnings.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20his%20opinion%20that%20Tesla%20should%20be%20valued%20more%20in%20line%20with%20other%20mega-cap%20tech%20names%2C%20Gerber%20said%20the%20stock%20should%20be%20trading%20around%20%24150%2C%20%26quot%3Bplus%20whatever%20fantastical%20valuation%20you%20want%20to%20put%20on%20taxis%20and%20robots.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-stock-price-prediction-ross-gerber-tax-bill-ev-credits-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752570901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d48d09585f1dff88b23f56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-stock-price-prediction-ross-gerber-tax-bill-ev-credits-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ross%20Gerber%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20nothing%20good%20for%20Tesla%26quot%3B%20in%20Trump's%20budget%20bill%2C%20and%20the%20stock%20should%20be%20trading%20more%20in%20line%20wi