0he%20suggests%20instead%20is%20that%20we%20tackle%20the%20systemic%20roots%20of%20the%20problem.%20His%20tenure%20as%20the%20district%20magistrate%20for%20two%20years%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Kokrajhar%20around%201986%20forms%20the%20bedrock%20of%20his%20suggestion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20many%20children%20who%20did%20not%20attend%20school%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20To%20Jhingran%2C%20this%20felt%20wrong%3B%20something%20that%20even%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98Right%20to%20Education%E2%80%99%20Act%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Act%20was%20enacted%20in%202009%20%E2%80%94%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20condone.%20%E2%80%9CI%20just%20felt%20that%20every%20child%20should%20be%20in%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20Years%20later%2C%20he%20would%20recall%20this%20sentiment%20as%20the%20precursor%20of%20his%20Delhi-based%20Language%20and%20Learning%20Foundation%2C%20which%2C%20since%20its%20inception%20in%202015%2C%20has%20helped%2014.2%20lakh%20children%20directly%20and%201.62%20crore%20children%20through%20indirect%20approaches%20(framing%20academic%20material).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEquitising%20education%20and%20creating%20a%20level%20playing%20field%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20bell%20goes%20off%20for%20teacher%20Smita%20Chaturvedi%E2%80%99s%20lessons%2C%20her%20students%20are%20exuberant.%20They%20love%20her%20lectures.%20Smita%20is%20well%20aware%20of%20how%20crucial%20a%20sound%20foundation%20is%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F135327%2Fkerala-out-of-box-solution-tribal-literacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%E2%80%99s%20academic%20milestones%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20she%20knows%20it%20can%20shape%20or%20break%20their%20futures.%20And%20so%2C%20she%E2%80%99s%20always%20attempted%20to%20breathe%20ingenuity%20into%20the%20topics%20she%20approaches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20for%20the%20better%20part%20