m%20poems%20and%20stories.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStories%20like%20these%20thrill%20Jhingran.%20It%E2%80%99s%20antithetical%20to%20the%20reality%20that%20he%20watched%20unfolding%20in%20the%20classrooms%20of%20Kokrajhar%20during%20his%20posting%20there.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20find%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F84823%2Fhow-reduce-illiteracy-rates-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20sitting%20passively%20in%20classrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20teacher%20would%20be%20doing%20the%20speaking%3B%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20the%20children%20were%20often%20even%20understanding%20what%20was%20happening.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20probing%20and%20conversations%20with%20the%20students%20revealed%20there%20was%20a%20language%20barrier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20children%20were%20used%20to%20speaking%20one%20language%20at%20home%20and%20were%20being%20taught%20in%20a%20different%20language%20in%20school.%20There%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jhingran%20adds%20that%20the%20paucity%20of%20educational%20facilities%2C%20compounded%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20most%20children%20only%20spoke%20the%20tribal%20dialect%2C%20was%20slow-rippling%20into%20illiteracy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy--1752495332.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dhir%20Jhingran%20is%20attempting%20to%20bridge%20the%20gaps%20that%20exist%20in%20foundational%20literacy%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-literacy--1752495332.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fdhir-jhingran-foundational-li