%20of%20place%20you%20stumble%20upon.%20To%20reach%20it%2C%20you%20have%20to%20leave%20your%20car%20behind%20and%20walk%20a%20stretch%20of%20narrow%20path%20that%20cuts%20through%20the%20slopes%20of%20Thathri%20village.%20There%20are%20no%20neon%20boards%20or%20manicured%20driveways%20here%2C%20only%20a%20cluster%20of%20mud%20and%20slate%20cottages%20rising%20gently%20from%20the%20earth%2C%20as%20though%20they%E2%80%99ve%20always%20belonged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20place%20frozen%20in%20tradition.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20retreat%20shaped%20with%20intention%2C%20a%20quiet%20rebellion%20against%20the%20pace%20and%20practices%20of%20mainstream%20tourism.%20Built%20almost%20entirely%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F361124%2Frammed-earth-timber-clay-sustainable-home-material-architecture-projects-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehandmade%20bricks%2C%20bamboo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20slate%2C%20Kosen%20Rufu%20is%20the%20result%20of%20years%20of%20labour%2C%20a%20deep%20personal%20calling%2C%20and%20the%20guidance%20of%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20revered%20eco-architects%2C%20Delia%20Kinzinger%20%E2%80%94%20known%20to%20many%20as%20Didi%20Contractor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183717.619-1752239561.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raman%20Siddhartha%20and%20Manju%20relocated%20from%20London%20to%20Dharamshala%20to%20build%20a%20sustainable%20homestay.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183717.619-1752239561.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183717.619-1752239561-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183717.619-1752239561-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183717.619-1752239561-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183717.619-1752239561-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-468158%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERaman%20Siddhartha%20and%20Manju%20relocated%20from%20London%20to%20Dharamshala%20to%20build%20a%20sustainable%20homestay.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%2C%20as%20it%20stands%20today%2C%20began%20as%20a%20piece%20of%20difficult%20terrain.%20It%20was%20constructed%20on%20a%20patch%20of%20land%20in%20Thathri%2C%20off%20Khanyara%20Road%20in%20Dharamshala%2C%20bought%20in%202018%20by%20filmmaker%20Raman%20Siddhartha.%20The%20idea%2C%20he%20says%2C%20was%20never%20about%20just%20building%20a%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20lived%20in%20London%20for%2025%20years%2C%20but%20I%20was%20born%20in%20Himachal.%20My%20father%2C%20a%20bureaucrat%2C%20took%20me%20to%20remote%20villages%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20grew%20up%20seeing%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ekachcha%20makaan%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mud%20homes)%20that%20were%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20the%20land%20and%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raman%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20never%20left%20me.%20It%20stayed%20in%20my%20subconscious%20that%20if%20I%20ever%20returned%2C%20I%20would%20build%20a%20mud%20house.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReturning%20to%20India%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20creative%20partner%20Manju%20Narayan%20in%202016%2C%20the%20couple%20initially%20explored%20the%20region%20as%20filmmakers.%20But%20the%20growing%20clutter%20of%20concrete%20homes%2C%20even%20in%20remote%20Himalayan%20corners%2C%20deeply%20unsettled%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20was%20in%20a%20rush%20to%20%E2%80%98develop%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manju%20says.%20%E2%80%9CConcrete%20everywhere.%20It%20felt%20like%20we%20were%20losing%20the%20soul%20of%20the%20land.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20build%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F445301%2Fkrithika-venkatesh-mud-homes-architecture-sustainable%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentirely%20sustainable%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20eventually%2C%20a%20homestay%2C%20began%20as%20a%20personal%20project.%20But%20soon%2C%20the%20scale%20and%20significance%20of%20what%20they%20were%20creating%20outgrew%20that%20scope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDidi%20Contractor%E2%80%99s%20architecture%20of%20resistance%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bring%20their%20vision%20to%20life%2C%20Raman%20and%20Manju%20reached%20out%20to%20Delia%20Kinzinger%2C%20the%20German-American%20architect%20better%20known%20in%20the%20region%20as%20Didi%20Contractor.%20Based%20in%20Dharamshala%2C%20Kinzinger%20had%20already%20spent%20decades%20building%20eco-sensitive%20homes%20that%20honoured%20local%20traditions%20and%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%2C%20by%20all%20accounts%2C%20uncompromising.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20refused%20to%20use%20AutoCAD%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raman%20says.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20sketch%20was%20hand-drawn.%20Every%20angle%20was%20measured%20by%20instinct%20and%20wisdom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20architect%20had%20her%20doubts%20initially.%20But%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20intention%2C%20sincerity%2C%20and%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20desire%20to%20reconnect%20to%20their%20roots%20eventually%20won%20her%20over.%20Her%20involvement%20changed%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20structures%20at%20Kosen%20Rufu%20were%20designed%20using%20mud%20bricks%20made%20from%20earth%20sourced%20locally%2C%20dried%20and%20shaped%20by%20hand.%20%E2%80%9CDrying%20them%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raman%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20mountain%20weather%20is%20unpredictable.%20Many%20bricks%20were%20washed%20away%20by%20sudden%20rain.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20long%20walk%20to%20sustainability%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20setbacks%2C%20they%20never%20resorted%20to%20cement.%20The%20foundation%20used%20bamboo%2C%20walls%20were%20packed%20with%20stone%20and%20mud%2C%20and%20even%20the%20roofing%20slate%20was%20locally%20quarried.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386103%2Fsustainable-architecture-in-india-green-pavers-cseb-earth-blocks-orient-stranded-board%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENo%20industrial%20material%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20brought%20in.%20The%20design%20incorporated%2018-inch%20thick%20walls%2C%20natural%20insulation%20using%20pine%20needles%20and%20dust%2C%20and%20multi-layered%20mud%20coatings%20that%20mimicked%20the%20strength%20of%20concrete%20%E2%80%94%20without%20the%20environmental%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183452.889_11zon-1752239828.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20design%20incorporated%2018-inch%20thick%20walls%2C%20natural%20insulation%20using%20pine%20needles%20and%20dust.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183452.889_11zon-1752239828.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183452.889_11zon-1752239828-300x157.jpg%203