ading%5C%22%3EFrom%20hostility%20to%20harmony%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20not%20everyone%20in%20Thathri%20was%20convinced.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20filed%20complaints%20against%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manju%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20anyone%20would%20build%20a%20mud%20house%20willingly%3B%20it%20was%20seen%20as%20something%20the%20poor%20do%20out%20of%20necessity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20beam%2C%20every%20brick%20at%20Kosen%20Rufu%20Village%20Recluse%20holds%20a%20story%2C%20not%20just%20of%20resistance%20to%20mainstream%20tourism%2C%20but%20of%20radical%20care%20for%20the%20land.%20One%20person%20who%20oversaw%20this%20careful%20dance%20between%20terrain%20and%20technique%20was%20the%20chief%20architect%20Naresh%20Sharma%2C%20who%20worked%20closely%20with%20both%20the%20founders%20and%20Delia%20Kinzinger%20to%20bring%20the%20retreat%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22No%20industrial%20material%20was%20used%20during%20the%20building%20of%20this%20sustainable%20home%20stay.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FT