%20a%20drip%20irrigation%20system.%20After%20this%2C%20she%20prepared%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F250491%2Fhow-to-grow-organic-tomatoes-up-woman-farmer-kanak-lata-success-story-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%20bed%20for%20tomatoes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20mulch%20(a%20layer%20of%20material%20applied%20to%20the%20surface%20of%20an%20area%20of%20soil%20to%20conserve%20soil%20moisture%20and%20improve%20fertility).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20experimenting%20and%20researching%20over%20the%20weekends%20between%202019%20and%202021%2C%20Smarika%20took%20the%20plunge%20into%20full-time%20farming.%20With%20seeds%20purchased%20from%20a%20local%20nursery%2C%20the%20Chandrakar%20family%20prepared%20for%20their%20first%20tomato%20harvest%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smarika%20plans%20to%20expand%20the%20area%20under%20vegetable%20cultivation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354729%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20clas