2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202021%2C%20she%20opened%20Cafe%20Aarambh%20in%20the%20leafy%20premises%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Environment%20Education%20(CEE)%20in%20Ahmedabad%E2%80%99s%20Thaltej%20area.%20Modest%20in%20scale%20but%20ambitious%20in%20philosophy%2C%20the%20cafe%20runs%20on%20a%20commitment%20to%20sustainable%20sourcing%2C%20zero%20waste%2C%20and%20a%20return%20to%20traditional%20and%20wholesome%20eating.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20carefully%20designed%20seasonal%20menu%20features%2015%20to%2020%20millet-based%20dishes%20that%20rotate%20based%20on%20seasonal%20availability%2C%20such%20as%20soft%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20dosas%2C%20pearl%20bhel%2C%20millet%20momos%2C%20a%3C%2Fem%3End%20a%20popular%20take%20on%20the%20classic%3Cem%3E%20vada%20pav%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eserved%20in%20freshly%20baked%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20buns.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meals%20are%20presented%20with%20the%20same%20thoughtfulness%20that%20goes%20into%20their%20preparation.%20Each%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F415426%2Fspice-up-foods-homemade-ready-eat-preservative-free-food-homemakers-meals-travellers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeal%20offers%20the%20comfort%20of%20a%20home-cooked%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20meals%20are%20served%20in%20glassware%2C%20completely%20avoiding%20plastic%20or%20any%20disposable%20clutter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20rare%20occasions%2C%20when%20single-use%20containers%20are%20needed%2C%20such%20as%20during%20takeaways%20or%20when%20food%20is%20served%20at%20external%20events%2C%20the%20cafe%20opts%20for%20biodegradable%20alternatives.%20Plates%20and%20bowls%20made%20from%20areca%20leaves%20or%20bagasse%2C%20both%20fully%20compostable%2C%20guarantee%20that%20convenience%20never%20comes%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20environment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20prefer%20to%20keep%20the%20menu%20small%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Nishtha.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20walk%20into%20most%20cafes%2C%20you%20see%20pages%20and%20pages%20of%20options.%20But%20here%2C%20we%20focus%20on%20dishes%20that%20are%20nourishing%20and%20connected%20to%20local%20traditions.%20It%20also%20means%20we%20avoid%20over-ordering%20ingredients%20or%20wasting%20what%20we%20cook.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EZero%20waste%20and%20maximum%20impact%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20intention%20carries%20through%20into%20the%20kitchen%2C%20where%20food%20is%20prepared%20each%20morning%20in%20limited%20quantities.%20Rather%20than%20guessing%20large%20numbers%2C%20the%20team%20carefully%20estimates%20how%20much%20will%20be%20needed%2C%20based%20on%20previous%20experience%20and%20the%20season%E2%80%99s%20demand.%20If%20a%20particular%20dish%20runs%20out%20before%20the%20day%20ends%2C%20it%20is%20removed%20from%20the%20menu%2C%20and%20no%20extra%20batches%20are%20prepared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20approach%20is%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20wastage%20and%20to%20create%20a%20sense%20of%20anticipation%20and%20appreciation%20among%20the%20cafe%E2%80%99s%20regulars.%20People%20come%20to%20the%20cafe%20not%20just%20to%20eat%2C%20but%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20system%20that%20values%20quality%20over%20quantity%2C%20and%20freshness%20over%20convenience.%20Each%20decision%2C%20from%20portion%20sizes%20to%20how%20leftovers%20are%20handled%2C%20reflects%20a%20larger%20ethic%20of%20responsibility.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F424409%2Fwhere-unsegregated-kitchen-waste-goes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleftover%20vegetable%20peels%20and%20wet%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20turned%20into%20compost%2C%20feeding%20the%20small%20but%20spirited%20kitchen%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebe